      • cancelReservation

        CancelReservationResponse cancelReservation​(Context context,
                                            CancelReservationRequest request)
                                     throws RemoteServiceException
        The entry point for canceling a held reservation to some remote authority. This method is invoked as part of the provisioning workflow, but directly from an explicit or implicit provision cancellation request.
        Parameters:
        context - The Context of the cancellation request
        request - The cancellation request in the CancelReservationRequest model
        Returns:
        The result of the method in the form of a CancelReservationResponse
        Throws:
        RemoteServiceException - Failure to cancel held reservation from a remote source
